<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Order Cancellation Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #f44336;
            /* Primary color: red */
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .order-details {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .order-items {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .order-items th,
        .order-items td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .order-items th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Order Cancellation Confirmation</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>
            <p>We have received your request to cancel your order with the tracking number
                <strong>{{trackingNumber}}</strong>, placed on <strong>{{orderDate}}</strong>. Your order has been
                successfully canceled. Below are the details of your canceled order:</p>

            <div class="order-details">
                <h3>Order Details</h3>
                <p><strong>Tracking Number:</strong> {{trackingNumber}}</p>
                <p><strong>Order Date:</strong> {{orderDate}}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="order-items">
                <h3>Order Items</h3>
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Item Name</th>
                            <th>Quantity</th>
                            <th>Price</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {{#each items}}
                        <tr>
                            <td>{{this.name}}</td>
                            <td>{{this.quantity}}</td>
                            <td>{{this.price}}</td>
                        </tr>
                        {{/each}}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>

            <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our customer
                support team. We apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused and appreciate your understanding.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for shopping with us. We hope to serve you again in the future.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>